{"tid":1378642,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"不合作運動，唔淨止MTR，仲有好多","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:08:09.000Z","uid":5271,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"026ef8dcb905e2e0fbcfca0acefc2e127f0f92d1","tid":1378642,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"亞美尼亞模式：和平守法與抗爭，有時沒有矛盾<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/120497\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F120497&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=fb3d9ec2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/120497</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟少少意見。<br />\n<br />\n每次咁多人出嚟集會，大部分嘅人都係齋企，等前線做嘢，雖然可以疊人數，但冇乜實際作用。有少少浪費人手。<br />\n<br />\n其實可以做好多合法事情。而唔會有衝突、唔使同狗硬碰。<br />\n<br />\n和理非、勇武都可以做，而且人數唔使好多，更可以分開係各區一齊做。<br />\n<br />\n1. 在香港，15米內沒有合適過路設施，中間又沒有欄杆路障，就可以直接橫過馬路<br />\n<br />\n2. 喜歡踩單車的人，也可以在馬路上合法騎行，只要保持單行<br />\n<br />\n3. 乘客搭地鐵也有權力及理由在月台靜候舒適和有空位可坐的列車<br />\n<br />\n4. 通往國際機場的道路（而非機場本身）變成停車場<br />\n<br />\n5. 免費幫路中心死火車輛修車<br />\n<br />\n6. 晚上在🐶🏠敲打廚具「發聲」<br />\n<br />\n等等有創意的方式<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 七大訴求缺一不可"},{"pid":"72ad5a0cd51e142095d0480a034b82cb91aa8ca7","tid":1378642,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:20:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3f189b38fbf258d11517e9579e56811087515e95","tid":1378642,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:20:37.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"3dc1a1049fc4a0b6ce394525d7e6528e0fa43ec1","tid":1378642,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"4aaf5d13f7111c7c7744a93fd14feb4aae73c340","tid":1378642,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:20:58.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"d382173e7040515d69c2796327cdeac762a2dbd5","tid":1378642,"uid":5271,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:21:11.000Z","msg":"港